1931-1932 - instructor, secretary of the executive committee of the Karaginsky district council (Kamchatka region). After the formation of the Koryaksky national district on December 10, 1930, he was elected the first chairman of the executive committee of the district Council of Workers' Deputies. Great Patriotic War [edit | edit code]
During the Great Patriotic War, he was a member of the State Defense Committee, a representative of the Headquarters for the formation of troops (September 1941 - February 1942) in the Far East. Post-war activities[edit | edit code]
He was elected a deputy of the Supreme Soviet of the USSR of the 1st-3rd convocations.